parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, as the airbags may not deploy properly or at all.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
airbags deploy unnecessarily
airbags fail to deploy in an accident
injuries or fatalities occur due to airbag malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of dealerships to properly repair or replace recalled airbag components can lead to continued risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: Dealerships fail to repair or replace recalled airbag components
parts are unavailable
dealerships do not provide loaner vehicles or alternative solutions
repairs are incomplete or inadequate.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lack of Communication and Customer Service
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Poor communication and customer service from dealerships and manufacturers can lead to frustration, delays, and continued risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: Dealerships and manufacturers fail to respond to customer inquiries
fail to provide updates on recall repairs
fail to provide loaner vehicles or alternative solutions
fail to acknowledge customer concerns.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear lights can increase the risk of a crash, as other drivers may not be able to see the vehicle's brake lights, turn signals, or tail lights.
symptoms: The rear lights
including brake lights
turn signals
and tail lights
fail to function or function intermittently
the warning light on the instrument panel illuminates
and there may be a burning smell or melted wires.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the turn signals can increase the risk of a crash, as other drivers may not be able to anticipate the vehicle's intentions.
symptoms: The turn signals fail to function or function intermittently
and there may be a burning smell or melted wires.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake lights can increase the risk of a crash, as other drivers may not be able to see that the vehicle is slowing or stopping.
symptoms: The brake lights fail to function or function intermittently
the warning light on the instrument panel illuminates
and there may be a burning smell or melted wires.
